text: Victoria Luz Cartagena is an American actress. She was born in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. Cartagena is known for her role as Zoe Lopez in The Bedford Diaries and as Renee Montoya in Gotham. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American stage actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Philadelphia
